{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":null,"total_pages":1,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2014-04-19T22:27:53Z","content":"I am signing this petition because I feel that everywhere should have vegetarian options","like_count":0,"author_name":"Adam Brass","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/90201487"},{"created_at":"2014-04-19T22:21:30Z","content":"Located on just about every street corner McDonald's boasts convenience at cheap prices and speedy service. Currently, the only vegetarian options they offer are french fries, or salads without chicken. Let's face it, you can't make a hearty meal out of either. Competing fast food restaurants such as Burger King and Harvey's offer a vegetarian burger option so why not McDonald's?! They shouldn't have to miss out on this part of the market if we can show them that there is in fact a demand!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jillian B","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/jillianb"}]}